data.description: Come see this cute home in the county that's still conveniently located to town amenities! This 1,128 square foot home features 3 bedrooms, a bath and a half, attached garage, and partial basement! Inside, you'll find a nice-sized living room with a large window equipped with plant shelves! Both bathrooms have been completely remodeled this year, with updated fixtures and a new rain head in the shower! As of 2023, updates include a new tankless water heater in October, new roof, new sump pump, new basement windows, and all new light fixtures. Schedule a showing today!
